 By definition, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int fd\mu=\sup\left\{ \sum_{j=1}^{m}\delta_{c}(A_{j})\inf_{A_{j}}f:\{A_{j}\}\text{ a \ensuremath{\Sigma}-partition}\right\} 
